window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>It's nothing personal. It's just business.</b> </p> <p>As a half demon, Cole Masters has been living a life with two sides. With every use of his Hellfire gift, he's brought closer to the monstrous Halfling within. He's spent years working with guns and killing for money, all to avoid the addictive corruption of his power and sedate the creature's need to destroy everything it touches. It's always been a temporary fix, but what he needs is a way to get this demon off his back for good.... </p> <p>When Cole finally gets the lead he's been searching for, he soon discovers it comes at a deadly price. One he isn't sure he's willing to pay. </p> <p><b>But without it, he's doomed to Hell.</b> </p> <p><i>Halfling for Hire</i> is a short story collection and a part of the Reaper Reborn Series and world. This collection includes:<i> Hell Bent, Hell Bound, Hell Fire, Hell Fury, and Hell Freed.</i> </p> <p><b>The Reaper Reborn Series </b></p> <p><b>#1</b><b><i> Death Wish </i></b></p> <p><b>#2</b><b><i> Death Trap </i></b></p> <p><b>#3</b><b><i> Death Match</i></b> </p> <p><b>#4</b><b><i> Death Deals</i></b> </p> <p><b>#5</b><b><i> Death Sentence </i></b></p> <p><b>#6 </b><b><i>Till Death </i></b></p> <p><b><i>Christmas Spirits (Special Edition Holiday Novella) </i></b></p> <p><b><i>Reaper Reborn Box Set: Books 1-3 </i></b></p> <p><b><i>Reaper Reborn Box Set: Books 4-6 </i></b></p> <p><b><i>Halfling for Hire: A Short Story Collection </i></b></p> <p><b><i>Tales of the Reborn: An Anthology</i></b></p>"; 
